Surface normals by Drew Smith

Adapted from vulkan-tutorial.com

Key bindings
p/P Toggle between orthogonal & perspective projection
m/M Stop/start light movement
-/+ Move light up/down
[/] Move light in orbit
arrows Change view angle
ESC Exit
